Author: DopamineDarling
Text: GET HELP! YOU ARE SICK ENOUGH! YOU ARE WORTH IT!  I've come all the way up to nearly dying and lying in a hospital bed on all sorts of machines saying "I'm not sick enough to deserve/need treatment" you will *never* feel sick enough, that's how this disease works. You have been expressing disordered behavior, even if you had gained weight that would still be a problem, please reach out and get help. You deserve it. Don't live this hell.
